	  Part No.: SAMV71J19, SAMV71J20, SAMV71J21, SAMV71N19, SAMV71N20,
	  SAMV71N21, SAMV71Q19, SAMV71Q20, SAMV71Q21, SAMV71J19B, SAMV71J20B,
	  SAMV71J21B, SAMV71N19B, SAMV71N20B, SAMV71N21B, SAMV71Q19B,
	  SAMV71Q20B, SAMV71Q21B
